title.narrative: Enhancing Nigeria's Response to HIV/AIDS - BDHC Lagos Freight

description.narrative: This activity (Enhancing Nigeria's Response to HIV/AIDS - BDHC Lagos Freight) is a component of Enhancing Nigeria's Response to HIV/AIDS reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £621,040. This component benefits Nigeria, and works in the following sector(s): Family planning, STD control including HIV/AIDS. , with the following implementing partners: Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office. The start date is 01-10-2009 and the end date is 01-09-2014.
